越南航空公司是一間完全由越南政府擁有的[[有限責任公司|有限責任公司]]，在2010年6月從越南航空總公司重組而成<ref name="Vietnam Airlines becomes limited liability company"/><ref>{{cite web|title= Vietnam Airlines|publisher= Centre for Aviation|url= http://www.centreforaviation.com/profiles/airlines/vietnam-airlines|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/69DvGLcTk?url=http://centreforaviation.com/profiles/airlines/vietnam-airlines|archivedate= 2012-07-17|accessdate= 2012-07-17|deadurl= yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title= List of Government-owned and Privatized Airlines (unofficial preliminary compilation)|publisher= [[International_Civil_Aviation_Organization|ICAO]]|date= 2008-07-04|url= http://legacy.icao.int/icao/en/atb/epm/ecp/PrivatizedAirlines.pdf|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/69DuvKwhD?url=http://legacy.icao.int/icao/en/atb/epm/ecp/PrivatizedAirlines.pdf|archivedate= 2012-07-17|accessdate= 2012-07-17|deadurl= yes}}</ref>{{rp|5}}，其職能是提高國家經濟收益，除了提供定期客貨及貨運航班服務外，還包括「對勞工負責、增加國家收入和提供包機服務」<ref name=JSTOR_2000/>。公司管理層由七人組成，全由[[越南總理|越南總理]]任命<ref name=JSTOR_2000/>。{{As of|2014|3}}，航空公司共僱用10,929名員工<ref name="SkyTeam & Members Fact Sheet"/>。越航總部搬到[[河內|河內]][[龍編郡|龍編郡]]前<ref name="About Us">{{cite web | title = About Us | publisher = Vietnam Airlines | url = http://www.vietnamairlines.com/wps/portal/en/site/about_us/our_background/!ut/p/c5/hY5LDoJAEAXPwgnm0QwMLIffAAIaohHZGBbGYARcGM8vuNIxaPeyUnnFGjb90D66c3vvxqG9spo1zjFQMuEiB9aO7YDi0FspKzRR8Ykf3rhLXgQqc2zSTAKKf9igrT9RRabIMytwSbNVUcQgsXNFFZUmYP_Z3s-1i-sqsX_yV93MsXASmq8V-ELj3_1lMvYndut3Nbr0wqVhPAFC4vMb/dl3/d3/L2dBISEvZ0FBIS9nQSEh/ | accessdate = 2009-10-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131005020217/http://www.vietnamairlines.com/wps/portal/en/site/about_us/our_background/%21ut/p/c5/hY5LDoJAEAXPwgnm0QwMLIffAAIaohHZGBbGYARcGM8vuNIxaPeyUnnFGjb90D66c3vvxqG9spo1zjFQMuEiB9aO7YDi0FspKzRR8Ykf3rhLXgQqc2zSTAKKf9igrT9RRabIMytwSbNVUcQgsXNFFZUmYP_Z3s-1i-sqsX_yV93MsXASmq8V-ELj3_1lMvYndut3Nbr0wqVhPAFC4vMb/dl3/d3/L2dBISEvZ0FBIS9nQSEh/ | archivedate = 2013-10-05 | deadurl = no }} "200 Nguyen Son Str., Long Bien Dist., Ha Noi city, Vietnam"</ref>，總部設在[[嘉林縣|嘉林縣]][[嘉林機場|嘉林機場]]<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20000311135317/http://www.vietnamair.com.vn/vnhome.htm|url=http://www.vietnamair.com.vn/vnhome.htm|title=Home page of VN_anh|publisher=Vietnam Airlines|archivedate=2000-03-11|accessdate=2010-12-21|quote=HEAD OFFICE: GIALAM AIRPORT, HANOI 10.000, VIETNAM.|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Directory: World Airlines|magazine=Flight International|issue=4927|volume=165|page=92|location=London|publisher=Reed Business Information|date=30 March – 5 April 2004|url=http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/2004/2004-09%20-%200335.html|accessdate=2010-12-21|quote=VIETNAM AIRLINES [VN] (HVN) Gialem Airport, Hanoi, Vietnam.|issn=0015-3710|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005123110/http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/2004/2004-09%20-%200335.html|archivedate=2013-10-05|deadurl=no|journal=}}</ref>。

===訓練===
2009年，越航與ESMA航空學院合作成立飛越飛行訓練公司（Bay Viet Flight Training Company），以便在越南本國訓練機師，目標為每年100名合資格畢業生<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.airbus.com/presscentre/pressreleases/press-release-detail/detail/airbus-supports-new-flight-training-school-in-vietnam/|title=Airbus supports new flight training school in Vietnam|date=2009-03-13|publisher=Airbus|accessdate=2013-08-07|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Igmje4qs?url=http://www.airbus.com/presscentre/pressreleases/press-release-detail/detail/airbus-supports-new-flight-training-school-in-vietnam/|archivedate=2013-08-07|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。2010年10月，越航計劃在2011至2012年間訓練出60名國籍機師，把國籍機師率由2010年的60%提升至2015年的75%，意味著2010至2015年間每年要訓練出至少100名機師<ref>{{cite news|title=Commercial pilots to be trained in Vietnam|publisher=VoV News|date=2010-10-16|url=http://english.vovnews.vn/Home/Commercial-pilots-to-be-trained-in-Vietnam/201010/120511.vov|accessdate=2010-10-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101227200518/http://english.vovnews.vn/Home/Commercial-pilots-to-be-trained-in-Vietnam/201010/120511.vov|archivedate=2010-12-27|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。此外越航亦與美國[[亞利桑那州|亞利桑那州]]的CAE航空學院簽定合同，把準機師送往當地培訓<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aviationpros.com/press_release/10632853/cae-global-academy-to-train-third-group-of-cadets-for-vietnam-airlines|title=CAE Global Academy to Train Third Group of Cadets for Vietnam Airlines|date=2012-02-23|publisher=Aviation Pros|accessdate=2013-08-07|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6IgnvlQXV?url=http://www.aviationpros.com/press_release/10632853/cae-global-academy-to-train-third-group-of-cadets-for-vietnam-airlines|archivedate=2013-08-07|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

===財政表現===
至1997年前，越航載客量每年平均上升37%，[[亞洲金融危機|亞洲金融危機]]爆發後，加上其它因素導致越航出現利潤損失，但越航在此期間仍能保持盈利。越航在1996年運載約250萬名旅客，比上一年增加了18%<ref name="FI1997-12" />，到2002年旅客量增加至400萬，同樣比上一次增加18%<ref name="profitsnumber">{{cite web|title=Coming of age|url=http://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/coming-of-age-176760/|work=Airline Business|date=2004-02-01|accessdate=2013-07-13|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6IRVAzWqH?url=http://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/coming-of-age-176760/|archivedate=2013-07-28|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，而貨運量則上升20%，使公司該年錄得3.577億美元利潤<ref name="profitsnumber"/>。

儘管[[嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症|SARS]]爆發，越航在2003年仍保持2.62億美元利潤。2006年，航空公司運載了680萬名旅客（370萬人在國際線），並在首11個月錄得近13.7億美元收入。2007年的表現更上一層樓，運量900萬人次旅客，其中400萬人次為國際航班，使公司錄得12.3億美元收入以及2300萬美元毛利；此外貨運吞吐量亦達11.51萬噸<ref>{{cite journal|author=Ballatyne, Tom|url=http://www.orientaviation.com/storage/PDF/OA%20Jul08/OAMag_V15N09_P30_CoverStory.pdf|title=Ambitious Vietnam aiming high|date=July–August 2008|page=31|journal=Orient Aviation|location=Beijing, China|publisher=Wilson Publishing HK|format=PDF|accessdate=2013-07-28|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6IRVIQ52M?url=http://www.orientaviation.com/storage/PDF/OA%20Jul08/OAMag_V15N09_P30_CoverStory.pdf|archivedate=2013-07-28|issn=1027-6572|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="Vietnam Airlines 2007 profit rises 6.4 pct" />。2009年，公司的收入為13億美元，比去年的15.6億美元略為下降，而旅客量為930萬人次<ref name="Vietnam Airlines 2009 profit falls 42 percent" />。根據Anna.aero報告，越航在2010年旅客運載量比去年上升了30%，使越南機場的旅客量上升約20%<ref name="VN_booming"/> 。2012年越航總收入為24億美元，並獲得3,300萬美元利潤<ref name="Restructuring">{{cite web|url=http://www.caa.gov.vn/eDefault.aspx?tabid=8&catid=506&articleid=9105|title=Vietnam Airlines to be restructured by 2015|date=2013-01-29|publisher=Civil Aviation Authority of Vietnam|accessdate=2013-07-10|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027074707/http://www.caa.gov.vn/eDefault.aspx?tabid=8&catid=506&articleid=9105|archivedate=2014-10-27}}</ref>；2013年毛利額達到2,500萬美元<ref name="Vietnam Airlines earns $25 million gross profit in 2013" />。

2012年2月，越南航空在越南國際線佔了40%市場<ref name="JPA_VNA">{{cite web|url=http://centreforaviation.com/analysis/jetstar-pacific-to-become-vietnam-airlines-low-cost-carrier-in-salutary-move-to-both-68641|title=Jetstar Pacific to become Vietnam Airlines' low-cost carrier in salutary move to both|date=2012-02-23|publisher=Centre for Aviation|accessdate=2013-07-25|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6IPbdbpU3?url=http://centreforaviation.com/analysis/jetstar-pacific-to-become-vietnam-airlines-low-cost-carrier-in-salutary-move-to-both-68641|archivedate=2013-07-27|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，以及77%國內線市場，另外14%國內線市場由捷星太平洋航空佔有<ref name=JPA_VNA/>，但到了12月越航的國內線市場下降至70%<ref name=Restructuring/>。

===子公司及附屬公司===
[[File:Vietnam_Airlines_Boeing_777-200ER_being_catered_@_SGN.jpg|thumb]]

越南航空公司擁有至少20間子公司和附屬公司<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vietnamairlines.com/wps/portal/en/site/about_us/subsidiaries_and_affiliates/|title=Subsidiaries & Affiliates|publisher=Vietnam Airlines|accessdate=2013-07-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131006025910/http://www.vietnamairlines.com/wps/portal/en/site/about_us/subsidiaries_and_affiliates|archivedate=2013-10-06|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。該公司預計將在2015年完成重組工作，並在同時出售名下超過10間公司的股份<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thanhniennews.com/index/pages/20130121-vietnam-airlines-to-go-private-start-restructuring-this-year.aspx|title=Vietnam Airlines plans IPO, to start restructuring this year|date=2013-01-21|work=Thanh Nien News|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6IPaz2abg?url=http://www.thanhniennews.com/index/pages/20130121-vietnam-airlines-to-go-private-start-restructuring-this-year.aspx|archivedate=2013-07-27|accessdate=2013-07-27|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。
