== 服務 ==
===機上娛樂===
越南航空有部分航班透過機上個人電視提供[[隨選視訊|隨選視訊]]（AVOD）服務。機上娛樂包括電影、遊戲、電視節目和音樂。越南航空亦提供兩個機上刊物——《Heritage》和《Heritage Fashion》，此外還有其它讀物。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vietnamairlines.com/wps/portal/en/site/the_experience/economy_class/inflight_entertainment/ |title=Inflight Entertainment |publisher=Vietnam Airlines |access-date=8 July 2013 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422021216/http://www.vietnamairlines.com/wps/portal/en/site/the_experience/economy_class/inflight_entertainment |archive-date=22 April 2014}}</ref>

===客艙===
;商務艙
[[商務艙|商務艙]]是越南航空三級座艙中最高級者。與其它航空公司的商務艙一樣，越航商務艙所提供的設施和服務均與經濟艙有所不同且更多。波音777的商務艙採用2-3-2排列方式，座距達62英寸，可向後傾157°<ref name=BC/><ref name="seat plan">{{cite web | title = Vietnam Airlines Boeing 777-200ER layout | publisher = Seat Expert | url = http://seatexpert.com/seatmap/355/Vietnam_Airlines_Boeing_777-200_(Three_class)/ | accessdate = 2010-03-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131030160459/http://seatexpert.com/seatmap/355/Vietnam_Airlines_Boeing_777-200_%28Three_class%29/ | archivedate = 2013-10-30 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，每個座位均設有10.4英寸可觸控個人電視，設有隨選視訊，在超過兩小時航班上提供免費熱食<ref name="BC">{{cite web | title = The Experience – Business Class | publisher = Vietnam Airlines | url = http://www.vietnamairlines.com/wps/portal/en/site/the_experience/business_class/seats/%21ut/p/c5/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3hnd0cPE3MfAwP_gEAzA08vN2PvEF9TA3d3c6B8JJK8u6-vm4GReaiFeZCrn6GBgSkB3V76Uek5-UlAe8JBNuNWa2CGV97AyQhNHotLQPIGOICjgb6fR35uqn5BbkRlsGeWCQAaUrfD/dl3/d3/L2dBISEvZ0FBIS9nQSEh/ | accessdate = 2010-03-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131004014714/http://www.vietnamairlines.com/wps/portal/en/site/the_experience/business_class/seats/%21ut/p/c5/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3hnd0cPE3MfAwP_gEAzA08vN2PvEF9TA3d3c6B8JJK8u6-vm4GReaiFeZCrn6GBgSkB3V76Uek5-UlAe8JBNuNWa2CGV97AyQhNHotLQPIGOICjgb6fR35uqn5BbkRlsGeWCQAaUrfD/dl3/d3/L2dBISEvZ0FBIS9nQSEh | archivedate = 2013-10-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

;豪華經濟艙
豪華經濟艙，即相當於[[優質經濟艙|優質經濟艙]]。豪華經濟艙的座距比經濟艙多，達36-38英寸，座位可向後傾7英寸<ref name="Seats – Deluxe Economy Class" />，排列方式為3-3-3<ref name="seat plan"/><ref name="flug">{{cite web | last = Thomalla | first = Volker K. | title = Vietnam Airlines Expands | publisher = ''Flug Revue'' (magazine) | date = September 2005 | url = http://www.flug-revue.rotor.com/FRheft/FRHeft05/FRH0509/FR0509c.htm | accessdate = 2010-04-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081114032413/http://www.flug-revue.rotor.com/FRheft/FRHeft05/FRH0509/FR0509c.htm | archivedate = 2008-11-14 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。豪華經濟艙只有部份波音777客機上設有。在超過90分鐘的航班均提供免費機上小食，在超過兩小時航班上則提供熱食<ref>{{cite web | title = Deluxe Economy Class | publisher = Vietnam Airlines | url = http://www.vietnamairlines.com.vn/wps/portal/en/site/the_experience/cabin_experience/deluxe_class/!ut/p/c5/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3hnd0cPE3MfAwMDZ2cLAyNzDx8T49BQQwMnc6B8JJK8u6-vG1A-1MI8yNXP0MDAlIBuL_2o9Jz8JKA94SCbcav1MkGTR7PJxBi_PMglIHkDHMDRQN_PIz83Vb8gN6Iy2DPLBABvk_Y7/dl3/d3/L3dDb0EvUU5RTGtBISEvWUZSdndBISEvNl9DR0FINDdMMDAwQ0M4MDI3SEw0M1VVMTBSMQ!!/ | accessdate = 2010-03-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111128033253/http://www.vietnamairlines.com.vn/wps/portal/en/site/the_experience/cabin_experience/deluxe_class/%21ut/p/c5/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3hnd0cPE3MfAwMDZ2cLAyNzDx8T49BQQwMnc6B8JJK8u6-vG1A-1MI8yNXP0MDAlIBuL_2o9Jz8JKA94SCbcav1MkGTR7PJxBi_PMglIHkDHMDRQN_PIz83Vb8gN6Iy2DPLBABvk_Y7/dl3/d3/L3dDb0EvUU5RTGtBISEvWUZSdndBISEvNl9DR0FINDdMMDAwQ0M4MDI3SEw0M1VVMTBSMQ%21%21 | archivedate = 2011-11-28 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

;經濟艙
所有型號客機均設有[[經濟艙|經濟艙]]，座位寬到由20英寸（A330）到20.9英寸（B777）<ref name="seat survey">{{cite web | last = Verghese | first = Vijay | title = Economy Class Seat Survey | publisher = Smart Travel | url = http://www.smarttravelasia.com/economy.htm | accessdate = 2010-03-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140330235926/http://www.smarttravelasia.com/economy.htm | archivedate = 2014-03-30 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，座距為31-32英寸，可向後傾6至13°（5-6英寸）<ref name="seat survey"/>。跟豪華經濟艙一樣，超過90分鐘的航班均提供免費機上小食，在超過兩小時航班上則提供熱食<ref>{{cite web | title = Economy Class | publisher = Vietnam Airlines | url = http://www.vietnamairlines.com.vn/wps/portal/en/site/the_experience/cabin_experience/economy_class/!ut/p/c5/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3hnd0cPE3MfAwMDZ2cLAyNzDx8T49BQQ4MgQ6B8JJK8u6-vG1A-1MI8yNXP0MDAlCTdaPJeJgR0e-lHpefkJwFdGQ5yN36TUOTR3GlijF8e5A-QvAEO4Gig7-eRn5uqX5AbGlEZ7Jll4qioCABDDDNz/dl3/d3/L3dDb0EvUU5RTGtBISEvWUZSdndBISEvNl9DR0FINDdMMDAwQ0M4MDI3SEw0M1VVMTA3NA!!/ | accessdate = 2010-03-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111128033258/http://www.vietnamairlines.com.vn/wps/portal/en/site/the_experience/cabin_experience/economy_class/%21ut/p/c5/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3hnd0cPE3MfAwMDZ2cLAyNzDx8T49BQQ4MgQ6B8JJK8u6-vG1A-1MI8yNXP0MDAlCTdaPJeJgR0e-lHpefkJwFdGQ5yN36TUOTR3GlijF8e5A-QvAEO4Gig7-eRn5uqX5AbGlEZ7Jll4qioCABDDDNz/dl3/d3/L3dDb0EvUU5RTGtBISEvWUZSdndBISEvNl9DR0FINDdMMDAwQ0M4MDI3SEw0M1VVMTA3NA%21%21 | archivedate = 2011-11-28 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

== 意外及事故 ==
{{main|{{link-en|越南航空意外及事故列表|List of Vietnam Airlines accidents and incidents}}}}
根據[[航空安全網|航空安全網]]資料，越南航空自1951年發生六宗事故，其中兩宗事故有人命傷亡<ref>{{cite web|title= Vietnam Airlines accident record|publisher= [[Aviation_Safety_Network|Aviation Safety Network]]|url= http://aviation-safety.net/database/operator/airline.php?var=6071|accessdate= 2013-07-28|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140203033438/http://aviation-safety.net/database/operator/airline.php?var=6071|archivedate= 2014-02-03|deadurl= no}}</ref>。兩宗致命意外均在五邊進場時發生，涉事飛機都是蘇製客機。最嚴重的意外是1997年9月3日一架圖-134B-3客機在[[金邊國際機場|金邊國際機場]]進場時撞樹墜毀，造成65人罹難<ref>{{ASN accident|title= VN-A120|id= 19970903-0|accessdate= 2011-10-26}}</ref>。另外一宗事故發生在1992年11月14日，一架[[雅克-40|雅克-40]]在芽莊機場進場時墜毀，機上31人只有1人生還<ref>{{ASN accident|title= VN-A449|id= 19921114-1|accessdate= 2011-10-26}}</ref>。此外1992年越航亦被劫機，但沒有造成人命損失<ref>{{ASN accident|type= Hijacking|id=19920904-1|accessdate= 2011-10-26}}</ref>。

